  "rationale": "This supervisor structure prioritizes rapid marker acquisition and approach, while ensuring obstacle avoidance and safe recovery. Helper states are introduced for committed actions (forward, rotate, scan, marker approach) to enforce one-shot behaviors and prevent oscillations. Marker tracking is prioritized when visible, and search alternates between short forward moves and scans. All uncontrollable events are handled in every state, with safety-critical events preempting actions. Terminal goal state is reached upon marker_close.",
