  "strategy": [
    "Prioritize marker_seen: immediately switch to marker_track and approach when visible.",
    "In marker_track, use move_to_marker as the only controllable; if marker_lost, switch to scan_full to reacquire.",
    "Upon marker_close, transition to goal_stop where only stop is enabled.",
    "In clear, alternate between forward_commit and scan_full to balance exploration and marker search.",
    "After any obstacle detection, transition to the corresponding obs_* state and use a preferred rotation to escape.",
    "After obstacle recovery, always pass through scan_full before resuming exploration.",
    "In obs_left, prefer rotate_commit_cw; in obs_right, prefer rotate_commit_ccw to avoid oscillations.",
    "All uncontrollable events are handled in every state; safety-critical events preempt actions.",
    "Helper commit states ensure one-shot actions and prevent infinite controllable loops.",
    "No move_forward is allowed from obs_front; recovery is via scan_full."
  ]
